      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Please do not take St. John's Wort with sertraline without consulting your doctor first. Combining these substances can lead to a dangerous condition called serotonin syndrome, which requires immediate medical attention. It is crucial that you discuss any changes to your medication or adding supplements with your prescribing physician who knows your full medical history. They can guide you on safe adjustments to your treatment plan for your stress and depression.",
