      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is always so busy and i can't really get an appointment before my finals start next week... plus st johns wort is just an herb, right? it's way more natural than the sertraline. surely a little bit won't cause a massive problem? i just really need something to help me get through this month.",
